snippet.title: Barbie Fashion Show - PC Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Barbie Fashion Show lets you help Barbie get ready for Fashion Week in Paris! 
Advance through 3 design studios, creating stylish outfits for Barbie and her four friends to model. 
It’s up to you to put on the coolest, most fashionable fashion shows ever!

Barbie Playlist:
